 situations, such as covering your flight costs to get home if a close family member passes away.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"best travel insurance hike\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best travel insurance hike\" class=\"wp-image-34594 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-1187x1536.jpg 1187w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113948\/best-travel-insurance-hike-791x1024.jpg 791w, https: