e if you get sick while traveling. No one can predict food poisoning or a broken ankle from hiking in the mountains, so it&#x2019;s essential to have insurance just in case. Traveling is one of the most exciting experiences, so don&#x2019;t end up losing all the money you have invested in your trip by not having travel insurance.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-safety\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">17 Tips to Travel Safe<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113944\/rainbow-mountain-hike.jpg\" alt=\"rainbow mountain hike\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rainbow mountain hike\" class=\"wp-image-34595 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113944\/rainbow-mountain-hike.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113944\/rainbow-mountain-hike-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113944\/rainbow-mountain-hike-600x451.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113944\/rainbow-mountain-hike-798x600.jpg 798w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23113944\/rainbow-mountain-hike-1078x810.jpg 1078w, https:\/