nd of person then you&#x2019;ll need very little cover. <\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33440&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113108\/best-travel-insurance.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113108\/best-travel-insurance-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113108\/best-travel-insurance-346x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Best Travel Insurances in 2022 (COVID-19 coverage)\" height=\"600\" width=\"346\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<p>However, if you are traveling with a camera, laptop, or expensive jewelry you will need a higher cover for this. Work out the value of all your belongings and check that the value the policy is willing to insure equals the same amount or more.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Have a look:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/camera-travel-photography\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Inside our camera bag<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear.jpg\" alt=\"insurance camera gear\"><\/noscript><img width=\"440\" height=\"338\" alt=\"insurance camera gear\" class=\"wp-image-34603 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-300x230.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-600x461.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-781x600.jpg 781w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-1054x810.jpg 1054w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-440x338.jpg 440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-1536x1180.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-163x125.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-234x180.jpg 234w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-768x590.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-1024x787.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-1406x1080.jpg 1406w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-1874x1440.jpg 1874w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113934\/insurance-camera-gear.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Make sure to check that the value is high enough in the &#x2018;lost luggage&#x2019; part of the policy. If an airline loses your baggage, it&#x2019;s good to check that the cover is high enough for all your belongings inside, and also the actual luggage itself.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"3-is-medical-care-part-of-your-travel-insurance\">3. Is medical care part of your travel insurance?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Travel insurance medical care is for &#x2018;emergency&#x2019; situations, rather than your regular day to day medical care. For example, if you eat some dodgy food in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/thailand\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Thailand<\/a> and get food poisoning, your travel insurance will cover you for any medical care you may need in the hospital. However, if you take regular medication, this is something you need to arrange before your trip as it&#x2019;s not classed as &#x2018;emergency&#x2019; care.&#xA0;(<a href=\"#best\">Here are the best travel insurances<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Relocating to a country for an extended period of time? An international health insurance will cover both emergency medical care and routine healthcare.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115850\/hanoi-street-food-market-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"hanoi street food market\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"hanoi street food market\" class=\"wp-image-31514 lazypreload\" data-sizes=