ript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-575x810.jpg\" alt=\"bali swing\"><\/noscript><img width=\"240\" height=\"338\" alt=\"bali swing\" class=\"wp-image-17875 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-575x810.jpg 575w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-300x423.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-600x846.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-240x338.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-426x600.jpg 426w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-545x768.jpg 545w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-726x1024.jpg 726w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-766x1080.jpg 766w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-1022x1440.jpg 1022w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1.jpg 1362w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125648\/bali-swing-1-575x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"understand-definitions\">Understand definitions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Check the meaning of certain definitions. For example, if you need to fly home due to the sudden death or injury of a &#x2018;close relative&#x2019;. Insurance providers may vary in their definition of what a &#x2018;close relative&#x2019; is. For instance, a parent or sibling may be covered but an auntie or cousin may not.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"don-t-be-irresponsible\">Don&#x2019;t be irresponsible<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Most policies will have general exclusions, where travelers will not be covered. For example, travelers will normally fail to claim if they are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Intoxicated due to alcohol or drugs.<\/li><li>Engaging in criminal, or illegal, activity.<\/li><li>Behaving in a reckless manner, or putting themselves in deliberate danger. For example, jumping off a cliff into the ocean, or driving off-road.<\/li><li>Claiming for belongings left unattended. Always make sure to keep belongings with you at all times, to avoid the risk of loss or theft.<\/li><li>Traveling with a pre-existing medical condition that they have not disclosed. Be honest and upfront with your insurance provider so you can get the best coverage for your needs.<\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"choose-an-insurance-provider-with-a-24-hour-hotline\">Choose an insurance provider with a 24-hour hotline<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This is essential so that you can call the provider any time day or night. You never know when you could run into trouble, especially if traveling in a different time zone to your insuring country. This is also really helpful if you need to ring to extend your policy or add coverage for new activities.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"use-comparison-websites-shop-around\">Use comparison websites &amp; shop around<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Don&#x2019;t just choose the first, cheap, coverage that you come across. Shop around, use comparison websites, and read reviews. This will guarantee you find the best deal and the best insurance for your needs.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Best travel insurance Do I need insurance? Choosing a travel insurance COVID-19 Things to remember 3 x Best Travel Insurances Every traveler has different needs. One may be traveling with expensive gear, so may need greater coverage for their belongings, and another may be skydiving and require higher coverage for activities. Take a look at [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":36243,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_relevanssi_hide_post":"","_relevanssi_pin_for_all":"","_relevanssi_pin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_unpin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_include_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_exclude_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_no_append":"","_relevanssi_related_not_related":"","_relevanssi_related_posts":"8510,21620,20269,13355,14849,13418"},"categories":[7172,30,9,7170],"tags":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v19.3 (Yoast SEO v19.7.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Best Travel Insurances in 2022 (COVID-19 coverage)<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"While traveling there is always the risk of the unexpected and it\u2019s best to be prepared 